  <refnamediv>
    <refname>imextendedmin</refname>
    <refpurpose>Extended-minima transform</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>


<refsynopsisdiv>
   <title>Calling Sequence</title>
   <synopsis>
   dstMat=imextendedmin(srcImg, Hmin);
   
   </synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection>
   <title>Parameters</title>
   <variablelist>
   <varlistentry><term>dstMat:</term>
      <listitem><para>Output binary image</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   <varlistentry><term>srcImg:</term>
      <listitem><para>Input image</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   <varlistentry><term>Hmin:</term>
      <listitem><para>h-maxima transform, specified as a positive scalar.</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
</refsection>

<refsection>
   <title>Description</title>
   <para>
The function computes the extended-minima transform, which is the regional minima of the H-minima transform.h is a nonnegative scalar.
   </para>
   <para>
</para>
</refsection>

<refsection>
